title: Ep. #113 | BTS's "Butter", Highlight's "NOT THE END", and OH MY GIRL's "Dun Dun Dance"
description:
Eric Nam is back one-on-one to talk the latest comeback hits in K-Pop from the past month (Highlight, BTS, Oh My Girl, pH-1 & Jamie, NCT). But before he gets into the songs, we catch up on what Eric's been up to with his new song release "Echo" with Armaan Malik and KHSMR for AAPI Celebration Month.

Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
